reviews.review_text: downloadable 64kbsMP3 I've been listening to one show from that day in GD history a day and only these AUD recordings and not the VBR zip files either, they're too big. Some sound better than other ones but they're all the Dead and I haven't listened to a bad show yet. That being said, this is a nice show, I liked it more than 5-3-91. The Speedway Boogie is a highlight, and a nice jam from Victim going into Crazy Fingers.Thanks for putting this on the Archives.
